org.jmxtrans.embedded.spring

Class EmbeddedJmxTransFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmxtrans.embedded.spring.EmbeddedJmxTransFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Aware, BeanNameAware, DisposableBean, FactoryBean<EmbeddedJmxTrans>, SelfNaming

    public class EmbeddedJmxTransFactory
extends Object
implements FactoryBean<EmbeddedJmxTrans>, DisposableBean, BeanNameAware, SelfNaming
    EmbeddedJmxTrans factory for Spring Framework integration.

    Default configurationUrls :

    • classpath:jmxtrans.json: expected to be provided by the application
    • classpath:org/jmxtrans/embedded/config/jmxtrans-internals.json: provided by jmxtrans jar for its internal monitoring
    Author:
    Cyrille Le Clerc
